 by car every morning, and then my son has to travel and take two different busses to come back home after school,\\\" Anne Maria said.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9970402556192444, \"rank\": 0.0028983606728414085, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"car\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"two different busses\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully there is something close by because just given how the daycares are run it's first come first serve,\\\" added Blake Meadows.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"score\": 0.7258354239452857, \"rank\": 0.37770709492801047, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the daycares\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2020, the BC NDP promised it would build the school in its campaign.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BC NDP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 9